Class SizeD

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.geometry.SizeD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISize, com.yworks.yfiles.utils.IStruct, Cloneable

    public final class SizeD
extends Object
implements com.yworks.yfiles.utils.IStruct, ISize
    An immutable ISize implementation to describe a size in two-dimensional space.
